Did that have contact information for people to massage Mr. Epstein? A. Yes, there was a page with the massages -- massage therapists for Palm Beach. Q. Was Jane's contact information in that book? A. Who? Q. Jane. A. No. Oh, excuse me. Can you repeat that? Q. The person we're referring to as Jane. A. Yes. Yes, it was. It was her on the contact information. Q. I want to make sure the record is clear here. Do you remember looking earlier at Government Exhibit 12 and telling us that you recognized that name? A. Yes. Q. And we're calling that person Jane? A. Yes. Q. That person, do you remember seeing her true name in this directory? A. Yes. SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300 DOJ-OGR-00012457
